{"tid":2120683,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"美斯等巴塞球員同家人疫情下外出度假,與政府建議相違背","createTime":"2020-07-22T23:54:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-22T23:58:37.000Z","uid":173952,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"438fb2eb87cba4e40705b884d243f88d88da8d5c","tid":2120683,"uid":173952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T23:54:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9Y7JgsA.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9Y7JgsA.png&h=e8c88621&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rzzzn7A.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Frzzzn7A.png&h=1130e9c5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n本月開始,西班牙就出現嚴重的公共衛生危機反彈的情況,其中加泰羅尼亞與阿拉貢是最嚴重的地區,過去一天西班牙全國確診超過500例,大部分在這兩個地區。<br />\n<br />\n而根據加泰大區政府7月17日發佈的政令,加泰羅尼亞和巴塞羅那多個地區已經進入封閉隔離狀態,加泰地區居民被建議,沒有特別需要,比如工作,就醫,購買日常用品,不要外出,更不要離開加泰大區。"},{"pid":"cd03fb0d54ce43e2be3ed7964eeedc6f09125abd","tid":2120683,"uid":173952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T23:55:47.000Z","msg":"諗起香港班廢老,連口罩都唔帶"},{"pid":"e16ff2364e080d17c1861729fd134adf1b0836a3","tid":2120683,"uid":43785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T23:56:27.000Z","msg":"佢見到大巴哪種完之後仲勁咗"},{"pid":"a05ff828a55c4b5d70539ea2992c0cf5e105a0bc","tid":2120683,"uid":173952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e16ff2364e080d17c1861729fd134adf1b0836a3","tid":2120683,"uid":43785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T23:56:27.000Z","msg":"佢見到大巴哪種完之後仲勁咗"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T23:58:37.000Z","msg":"個別例子..."}]}